               </tr>
            </tbody>
         </table><p></p><p></p></level1><level1><h1>1. The Title you offer</h1><p></p><table border="1">
            <tbody>
               <tr>
                  <td><p>Introduction</p></td>
                  <td><p>Interesting facts, examples or quotations that logically point to the subject.</p><p>(Can be considered as argumentation for the article to be written and read)</p></td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                  <td><p>Situation/ Problem described</p></td>
                  <td><p>Describe the situation when you faced the problem. And the problem itself.</p><p>Talk about existing trends/problems in this or that area.</p><p>You can ask a question (or two) that will be answered in the article.</p></td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                  <td><p>Solution</p></td>
                  <td><p>Explain how to solve the problem/ answer the question/ avoid such problems. Give valuable advice. Provide with important/ interesting information</p></td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                  <td><p>A few words about GS</p></td>
                  <td><p>How we at Gersis-Software solve the problem. </p><p>When we face similar problems/situations.</p><p>How we treat our customers in such situations.</p></td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                  <td><p></p></td>
                  <td><p></p></td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                  <td><p>Additional info sources</p></td>
                  <td><p xml:lang="en-GB">Articles, links, people etc.</p><p></p></td>
               </tr>
            </tbody>
